/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4af6d8421c84d03070e3bbc3af869568621fa22","tid":465762,"uid":80323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T14:19:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>下隻超三a 大作係幾時呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ncrysis我諗係前無古人後無來者既game，好可能以後都唔會再有。<br />\n一黎PC獨佔3A大作少(同年隻Witcher 1唔知算唔算)。<br />\n二黎出續作既時候可能會轉做跨平台，crysis同witcher都係咁。出得跨平台又要就返家用機機能。<br />\n第三，就算出PC獨佔3A大作都未必會出隻超前幾年，超出當時硬件性能既game，witcher 2最初都係PC獨佔，都無好似crysis咁超前幾年。<br />\n<br />\n講到witcher，crysis同witcher兩個遊戲系列同工作室既結果真係好唔同。兩個系列都係07年出，兩個<span style=\"color: red;\">都係</span>由PC獨佔轉做跨平台，witcher轉做跨平台之後人氣同銷量都大升，crysis就反而仲差<span style=\"color: red;\">左</span>咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a20405d186eb20fa1cc78661000358e6c7254b30","tid":465762,"uid":64578,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T14:22:02.000Z","msg":"有冇人記得half-life2？ 果陣時呢隻又係跨世代作品，重力槍果d，果陣一個試玩版都玩左幾十次"},{"pid":"1e97ddd1b82bb2af3df6dbc09b2df9e9f48c805f","tid":465762,"uid":4526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T14:25:24.000Z","msg":"喺十年前就已經做到而家都唔係個個都做得到嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d12ccc4bc826a70fc79c94f615a260c9b1cc592","tid":465762,"uid":83340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T14:35:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人記得half-life2？ 果陣時呢隻又係跨世代作品，重力槍果d，果陣一個試玩版都玩左幾十次</blockquote><br />\nHL2 既source engine果陣真係震撼到，細細個用住部Pentium III 64mb ram既電腦，睇住d demo片真係J出血"},{"pid":"59ac93a7fc9f967be710d6609e34b8d42cca5c7d","tid":465762,"uid":39521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T14:36:55.000Z","msg":"真心冇玩過crysis1同warhead，嗰時太細個屋企人比嘅budget只可以推得郁crysis2，所以第一隻玩嘅係就係佢，但佢優化做得好神，就算垃圾機玩都覺得畫質好正，加上鍾意城市環境多過荒島，所以以前真係試過crysis2玩二週目收集晒所有item<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw其實而家過咗咁多年睇翻轉頭2代只係一隻不過不失嘅game，最深刻嘅就係prophet句remember me同埋han zimmer首theme，劇情都記得五六成，3代係垃圾到直頭玩完冇晒印象，最多就係爆水壩<br />\n<br />\n首theme真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Iy4iQvJo24U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIy4iQvJo24U&d=NPHxMgBctKn2sglCROAhpzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=e6a6d280\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Iy4iQvJo24U</a>"},{"pid":"82f0ca992669724e2f7fea05d292a37c32d50690","tid":465762,"uid":31178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T14:42:32.000Z","msg":"1集好多載具好正"},{"pid":"c58bbb8b43944346972088e4badbf4a240b5aab1","tid":465762,"uid":134834,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T14:53:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇人記得half-life2？ 果陣時呢隻又係跨世代作品，重力槍果d，果陣一個試玩版都玩左幾十次</blockquote><br />\nHL2 既source engine果陣真係震撼到，細細個用住部Pentium III 64mb ram既電腦，睇住d demo片真係J出血</blockquote><br />\nHL2個引擎真係劃時代<br />\n以標準來講<br />\n個物理系統係超撚晒班<br />\n加埋valve自家幾隻皇牌<br />\n影響力可以稱得上係遊戲界一個重要里程碑<br />\nCrysis純硬體追求<br />\n門檻高令到佢好小眾<br />\n不過佢都對往後fps畫面上既細節都有深遠影響"},{"pid":"70da766531959435f3bbdca7b1729a1e32f04c6c","tid":465762,"uid":134834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T14:54:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇人記得half-life2？ 果陣時呢隻又係跨世代作品，重力槍果d，果陣一個試玩版都玩左幾十次</blockquote><br />\nHL2 既source engine果陣真係震撼到，細細個用住部Pentium III 64mb ram既電腦，睇住d demo片真係J出血</blockquote><br />\nHL2個引擎真係劃時代<br />\n以當時標準來講<br />\n個物理系統係超撚晒班<br />\n加埋valve自家幾隻皇牌<br />\n影響力可以稱得上係遊戲界一個重要里程碑<br />\nCrysis純硬體追求<br />\n門檻高令到佢好小眾<br />\n不過佢都對往後fps畫面上既細節都有深遠影響</blockquote>"},{"pid":"8c9bbfd1eab2411c67dadf4a6c691a0cb2de0f12","tid":465762,"uid":29625,"like":3,"di