ets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再下一次俾畫面震撼到已經要數到4年後 Battlefield 3個Frostbite engine</blockquote><br />\n第一次震撼HL2<br />\n第二次Crysis<br />\n第三次BF3<br />\n打後d game 好似到左樽頸，畫面靚左dd, 但冇劃時代既震撼感"},{"pid":"0f46fde0b46ed3d91ce9da833d5c9ccbb96a2cd9","tid":465762,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T15:11:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>經典硬件殺手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再下一次俾畫面震撼到已經要數到4年後 Battlefield 3個Frostbite engine</blockquote><br />\n第一次震撼HL2<br />\n第二次Crysis<br />\n第三次BF3<br />\n打後d game 好似到左樽頸，畫面靚左dd, 但冇劃時代既震撼感</blockquote><br />\n發展到而家有時真係分唔到真定假，諗唔到仲可以點突破<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737dc139d8deb7ff6a916b84635f0704b89a4f02","tid":465762,"uid":60764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T15:11:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea2fe78039bc14f11c1292476f607d949485394b","tid":465762,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T15:11:55.000Z","msg":"果陣部機太廢玩唔撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3f44130c1955e1b6cfa9e8e9e1d1a7e0bc5a6b3","tid":465762,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T15:15:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>下隻超三a 大作係幾時呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ncrysis我諗係前無古人後無來者既game，好可能以後都唔會再有。<br />\n一黎PC獨佔3A大作少(同年隻Witcher 1唔知算唔算)。<br />\n二黎出續作既時候可能會轉做跨平台，crysis同witcher都係咁。出得跨平台又要就返家用機機能。<br />\n第三，就算出PC獨佔3A大作都未必會出隻超前幾年，超出當時硬件性能既game，witcher 2最初都係PC獨佔，都無好似crysis咁超前幾年。<br />\n<br />\n講到witcher，crysis同witcher兩個遊戲系列同工作室既結果真係好唔同。兩個系列都係07年出，兩個<span style=\"color: red;\">都係</span>由PC獨佔轉做跨平台，witcher轉做跨平台之後人氣同銷量都大升，crysis就反而仲差<span style=\"color: red;\">左</span>咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n我諗續作本身嘅內容先係主要原因"},{"pid":"d92a585f9f5378a650b1b7213c6837046ce19ee6","tid":465762,"uid":22682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T15:20:07.000Z","msg":"第一集+Warhead嘅MP最好玩.. 之後幾集就COD上身"},{"pid":"39200bad0586cd8e6ad5da16f29fe091d3846da9","tid":465762,"uid":80323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T15:36:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇人記得half-life2？ 果陣時呢隻又係跨世代作品，重力槍果d，果陣一個試玩版都玩左幾十次</blockquote><br />\nHL2 既source engine果陣真係震撼到，細細個用住部Pentium III 64mb ram既電腦，睇住d demo片真係J出血</blockquote><br />\nHL2個引擎真係劃時代<br />\n以當時標準來講<br />\n個物理系統係超撚晒班<br />\n加埋valve自家幾隻皇牌<br />\n影響力可以稱得上係遊戲界一個重要里程碑<br />\nCrysis純硬體追求<br />\n門檻高令到佢好小眾<br />\n不過佢都對往後fps畫面上既細節都有深遠影響</blockquote><br />\nhalf life 2同年出左隻far cry，far cry先係Crytek第一隻game。同half life 2有冇得鬥?<br />\n兩隻都未玩過"},{"pid":"10f8dbb7e0a8d2aa6fba2692b32f1b1c5212e834","tid":465762,"uid":51308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T15:40:45.000Z","msg":"有名你叫<br />\n<br />\n顯卡危機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d19a295b8a556f0e9d479b0fc4dde7e6938dc6","tid":465762,"uid":59252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T15:47:44.000Z","msg":"當年顯卡殺手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> CanYouRunIt既Top search就係Crysis<br />\n我仲記得出Crysis2果時我部機先玩到第一集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第3集把弓好撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade8478a0f870b1a8839aeae0964ba7767c6598e","tid":465762,"uid":16283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T15:49:40.000Z","msg":"玩crysis果陣岩岩出2<br />\n之後追埋3<br />\n真係好正"},{"pid":"4687e7cf9c746eb2a63724c9456f3ac2835ed96e","tid":465762,"uid":16283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T15:50:26.000Z","msg":"好記得果陣crysis係被譽為顯示卡殺手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f260026f36fc329c88ef96401dabb6fee8412aa1","tid":465762,"uid":137120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T16:07:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>經典硬件殺手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再下一次俾畫面震撼到已經要數到4年後 Battlefield 3個Frostbite engine</blockquote><br />\nBattlefield 真係世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71571d354ca089a2b7c808282a45679dddc96c99","tid":465762,"uid":35815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T16:14:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff9ed8dd371a248ccbf63de34bf2e27bfad069a5","tid":465762,"uid":55725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T16:27:25.000Z","msg":"10年之後我張980ti玩crysis有啲&quot;問題&quot;<br />\nNvidia真係無撚敵"},{"pid":"bb69b5f647df666faa6b14cfa8d47a50f8df1576","tid":465762,"uid":68325,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T16:36:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇人記得half-life2？ 果陣時呢隻又係跨世代作品，重力槍果d，果陣一個試玩版都玩左幾十次</blockquote><br />\nHL2 既source engine果陣真係震撼到，細細個用住部Pentium III 64mb ram既電腦，睇住d demo片真係J出血</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nhl系列更甚者喺佢作為fps但劇情精彩絕倫，即使呢一刻再玩仍然徹徹底底唔覺過時（更有source engine物理效果加持），類近嘅前少少quake劇情上絕對去唔到hl果個成就,一路殺到底仍然喺主要部份<br />\n不過追開嘅同好估計都大概知道hl3近況<br />\n<br />\n另一方面source engine衍生出龐大mod社群亦都唔可以忽視，無論喺cs主軸系列定旁支；而且講緊喺十幾年前，可謂繼quake mod熱潮後另一個新時代熱潮，建基喺畫面上嘅飛躍進步<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多謝quake多謝valve更要多謝quake年代普及wasd果位香港人慰及大多數後來嘅gamer<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"263ecd0c7324b247e0c3c61359191a346585786c","tid":465762,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T16:39:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢十年aaa game dev team 俾堆智障手機課金垃圾搞散晒<br />\n<br />\nGta v 之後已經無進步過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 智障手機課金垃圾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一隻game 最多賣500 連埋dlc 千幾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n堆強國土豪  件件6位，7位咁課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"120cc4e6646e4d77267a5e286d64e291092f63d2","tid":465762,"uid":131423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T16:59:34.000Z","msg":"一開始係玩crysis 2<br />\n開game 個句achieved by cryengine 3已經好型"},{"pid":"0205f1c7c88abe00ee1d92da6296758a6f32140d","tid":465762,"uid":24345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T17:00:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好期待gta 6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好撚提，因為gta online 搞到single player dlc都冇撚埋，好撚戇鳩"},{"pid":"1fec497753548a183233b46d9b3ef32682558149","tid":465762,"uid":50766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T17:03:00.000Z","msg":"其實crysis個故事係咪已經完哂？好想佢出第4集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f8e208cd5552bf178ccac67bb5e261f2811d003","tid":465762,"uid":53522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T17:07:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e76355aa852bfdaa1a2ab0c711ebc723584abd","tid":465762,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T17:10:40.000Z","msg":"依家用電腦開4k + ultra已經覺得好真實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係諗唔到可以點再進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"778dce725c9997220fa8c1ba93fa74631ab8dc8c","tid":465762,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T17:13:18.000Z","msg":"咁就十年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b70b3f9e776aed56de1564fc67fd00ac6f5354e","tid":465762,"uid":86938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T17:14:37.000Z","msg":"我記得CRYSIS只係用黎推銷佢副引擎既副產品嚟"},{"pid":"40fd16213098cc0f65186c0578482a3844cc06dd","tid":465762,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T17:22:10.000Z","msg":"已爆晒3集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e300cde54c0fabc8cc8da56583c3912acc893dac","tid":465762,"uid":68215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T17:35:34.000Z","msg":"好似宜家好多研發都係集中喺開放世界上面<br />\n好似Star Citizen 咁<br />\n對運算能力好高要求<br />\n反而對畫質要求無乜大突破"},{"pid":"bde15d6982e5586a2b5d7d1ed3a9e038999109d0","tid":465762,"uid":51944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T17:40:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>果陣部機太廢玩唔撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n夾硬開game玩到熄機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 算體驗過下幾震撼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c0119390acf66b6aa6a5fc08338fec91c00053f","tid":465762,"uid":9712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T17:41:33.000Z","msg":"游出海游遠啲的話，會俾鯊魚咬死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3d69e9f144954d069ed7a99c0ec926b72077edb","tid":465762,"uid":9284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T17:45:55.000Z","msg":"相比之下依加pubg好垃圾"},{"pid":"76e9a9fa26971f2dcb1713270add94dd7f9547ce","tid":465762,"uid":68325,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T18:12:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似宜家好多研發都係集中喺開放世界上面<br />\n好似Star Citizen 咁<br />\n對運算能力好高要求<br />\n反而對畫質要求無乜大突破</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n實際上舊如cs系列，多人環境下(如&gt;30 active players)同樣已經對cpu開始構成負擔(大量人物/物件或動態光影物理運算)，莫論60players或以上，故此source engine喺近乎只行cpu單春情況下每每令fps drop時常發生<br />\n<br />\n而更甚者部份時下熱門遊戲仍然只有dx9模式,framerate可想而知<br />\n<br />\n多年以嚟各式各樣因素都直接或者間接導致好多引擎都唔太上心multithread,但願推向民用6core以上嘅cpu界會帶領埋遊戲界喺未來願意付出更多時間或財力去基於多春cpu調校遊戲表現， 甚至改變起於遊戲引擎自身<br />\n<br />\n最後得著最多嚟得最易固然喺所有玩家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7f3e85d19e328f3d3ce5a83d0b65cd0af92272","tid":465762,"uid":1065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T18:37:55.000Z","msg":"加埋mod真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.moddb.com/images/mods/1/23/22309/Level01-03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.moddb.com%2Fimages%2Fmods%2F1%2F23%2F22309%2FLevel01-03.jpg&h=2064ab91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.moddb.com/images/mods/1/23/22309/Level01-02.3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.moddb.com%2Fimages%2Fmods%2F1%2F23%2F22309%2FLevel01-02.3.jpg&h=06b06b6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.moddb.com/images/mods/1/23/22309/Level03-01.3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.moddb.com%2Fimages%2Fmods%2F1%2F23%2F22309%2FLevel03-01.3.jpg&h=8ddb6523&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.moddb.com/images/mods/1/23/22309/Level04-02.2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.moddb.com%2Fimages%2Fmods%2F1%2F23%2F22309%2FLevel04-02.2.jpg&h=d735d8e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2007257db103b727e3ab11e1e3a5eec1cae7ab4","tid":465762,"uid":53378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T18:39:59.000Z","msg":"當年部機唔夠勁run唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c9d0307e0fa8641673ebe2c2d8f81bd4858581","tid":465762,"uid":127716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T18:51:42.000Z","msg":"顯卡殺手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84a442959b6fe3a19e53c178161bac2e14d1a425","tid":465762,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T19:29:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實crysis個故事係咪已經完哂？好想佢出第4集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n間廠好撚慘 紅game唔紅廠 好似話就黎破產 仲要拖員工五個月人工"},{"pid":"cb120e466cafdc6e427872a7e9cfac5edaa1c49a","tid":465762,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T19:30:06.000Z","msg":"好多game用晒Unreal / Unity<br />\n冇人用CryEngine<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4247d7060e484c8fd37c732817633d17ed4c0c3","tid":465762,"uid":39521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T22:50:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇人記得half-life2？ 果陣時呢隻又係跨世代作品，重力槍果d，果陣一個試玩版都玩左幾十次</blockquote><br />\nHL2 既source engine果陣真係震撼到，細細個用住部Pentium III 64mb ram既電腦，睇住d demo片真係J出血</blockquote><br />\nHL2個引擎真係劃時代<br />\n以當時標準來講<br />\n個物理系統係超撚晒班<br />\n加埋valve自家幾隻皇牌<br />\n影響力可以稱得上係遊戲界一個重要里程碑<br />\nCrysis純硬體追求<br />\n門檻高令到佢好小眾<br />\n不過佢都對往後fps畫面上既細節都有深遠影響</blockquote><br />\nhalf life 2同年出左隻far cry，far cry先係Crytek第一隻game。同half life 2有冇得鬥?<br />\n兩隻都未玩過</blockquote><br />\nfar cry要去到3代先真正高峰<br />\nvaas條痴線佬好正"},{"pid":"39227a5a681f03f3f4cdd9e3264ef50635765ff0","tid":465762,"uid":42064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T00:30:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多game用晒Unreal / Unity<br />\n冇人用CryEngine<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果佢出返隻易寫game嘅engine就得。<br />\nUnity個形象太貼地，雖然其實Cryengine都免費俾普通人用，但冇乜人用嚟寫indie。"},{"pid":"d1fb2854555b3d1fbc17121bd132d7fc41a67d9a","tid":465762,"uid":80323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T00:39:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實crysis個故事係咪已經完哂？好想佢出第4集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n間廠好撚慘 紅game唔紅廠 好似話就黎破產 仲要拖員工五個月人工</blockquote><br />\n上年年底已經關閉所有工作室，淨係保留核心團隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"939ea3d792d77266f8ed70ce333553dd8725f11a","tid":465762,"uid":64578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:40:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇人記得half-life2？ 果陣時呢隻又係跨世代作品，重力槍果d，果陣一個試玩版都玩左幾十次</blockquote><br />\nHL2 既source engine果陣真係震撼到，細細個用住部Pentium III 64mb ram既電腦，睇住d demo片真係J出血</blockquote><br />\nHL2個引擎真係劃時代<br />\n以當時標準來講<br />\n個物理系統係超撚晒班<br />\n加埋valve自家幾隻皇牌<br />\n影響力可以稱得上係遊戲界一個重要里程碑<br />\nCrysis純硬體追求<br />\n門檻高令到佢好小眾<br />\n不過佢都對往後fps畫面上既細節都有深遠影響</blockquote><br />\nhalf life 2同年出左隻far cry，far cry先係Crytek第一隻game。同half life 2有冇得鬥?<br />\n兩隻都未玩過</blockquote><br />\nfar cry要去到3代先真正高峰<br />\nvaas條痴線佬好正</blockquote><br />\nfar cry 4專登買980去玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"222107e18555609b03d21b8b61377a25fa57481a","tid":465762,"uid":35328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T05:16:58.000Z","msg":"玩過晒123代，感覺1代係最好玩，<br />\n23代劇情短，不過而家唔記得晒佢地點玩，<br />\ncrysis 3係我暫時最後一隻game買實體碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n而家仲會唔會有人買PC碟黎買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n提起hl3就想屌到valve反皮，<br />\n知近況嘅巴打都知hl原作家連故仔都post埋出嚟，<br />\n07年出orange box，到而家10年，<br />\nhl3 除咗啲concept art rumor之外就冇聲氣，<br />\nvalve而家賣dota 2 csgo tf2 賺到fat fat，<br />\n可唔可以還我當年會做好game嘅 valve<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你出hl3，我多多錢都買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92b7f1f55bddd6bec120463e8a8cdbd42022aee5","tid":465762,"uid":80323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T06:03:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好多game用晒Unreal / Unity<br />\n冇人用CryEngine<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果佢出返隻易寫game嘅engine就得。<br />\nUnity個形象太貼地，雖然其實Cryengine都免費俾普通人用，但冇乜人用嚟寫indie。</blockquote><br />\nUnity本身就唔係for 3A大作，應該係for低技術/小遊戲。Unreal本身應該係for 3A大作/高技術game，但係都有唔少中低技術game用。<br />\n而cryengine真係少人用，我暫時淨係見Prey用"},{"pid":"7e346cf6956680710e1455adbe8350e9d0909b23","tid":465762,"uid":80323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T10:35:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好似宜家好多研發都係集中喺開放世界上面<br />\n好似Star Citizen 咁<br />\n對運算能力好高要求<br />\n反而對畫質要求無乜大突破</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n實際上舊如cs系列，多人環境下(如&gt;30 active players)同樣已經對cpu開始構成負擔(大量人物/物件或動態光影物理運算)，莫論60players或以上，故此source engine喺近乎只行cpu單春情況下每每令fps drop時常發生<br />\n<br />\n而更甚者部份時下熱門遊戲仍然只有dx9模式,framerate可想而知<br />\n<br />\n多年以嚟各式各樣因素都直接或者間接導致好多引擎都唔太上心multithread,但願推向民用6core以上嘅cpu界會帶領埋遊戲界喺未來願意付出更多時間或財力去基於多春cpu調校遊戲表現， 甚至改變起於遊戲引擎自身<br />\n<br />\n最後得著最多嚟得最易固然喺所有玩家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依加既cpu性能應該夠，問題係ps4同xbox one既cpu太廢(聽聞仲廢過i3)<br />\n<br />\n得dx9既遊戲應該係D低技術遊戲，3A大作唔會得dx9既"},{"pid":"67e631f39f6c6de99e53d3b0206b28bb3ab29daf","tid":465762,"uid":15877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T10:47:10.000Z","msg":"顯卡危機"}]}